                    <h2>ABOUT ME</h2>

                    <p>

                    <img src="http://www.pastrypal.com/wp-content/themes/5pastrypal/images/avatar.jpg" align="left" style="padding-right:15px; padding-top:5px;"/>

                    After working in advertising for a few years, I got the crazy idea that I wanted to start over and become a pastry chef. And for 8 years that's exactly what I did, working in some of the best fine dining restaurants in New York City. Though I'm now semi-retired from the professional kitchen,  I still love to bake (and teach) at home. With this blog, I want to make great desserts for my own delicious good time and also show you how to get a great result with step-by-step photos. So get out your rolling pin and join in.</p>

